@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tfaddr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (((v1 + 0.16 / v0 + 0.67) * v2) * v2)
    tmp = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.05) * (tmp + 0.62 * v1 + 0.09)) + ((v0 + 0.53 - v2 + 0.72) + 0.80))
    v1 = 0.59
    tmp = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
